For any $m\in{\mathbb{Z}}^{d}$ with $0<|m|<N_{j-1}$, define $$\label{e.lambdamjdef}
        \Lambda_{m}(j) = \left\{ e^{it} \in \Sigma : \left\Vert 2 \rho\left( 2\Phi, D_{\phi(t)}^{j-1}e^{f^{j-1}_{t}}\right)- \langle m, 2\Phi \rangle \right\Vert_{{\mathbb{R}}/{\mathbb{Z}}} < \epsilon_{j-1}^{\frac{1}{15}}  \right\},$$ and $$\label{e.Kjdef}
